subSubSection.paragraph:
Distribution. The species has been reported previously from Costa Rica ,
Guatemala
and
Panama
( Sanborn 2013 ; 2014). Panamanian specimens are from Barro Colorado Island,
Panama
Canal Zone, 120 m altitude in lowland forest ( Ramos & Wolda 1985 ; Wolda 1977 ; 1988 ; 1989 ; Wolda & Ramos 1992 ).
